# title ------------------------------------------

# Add: adding a feature
# Remove: removing a feature
# Fix: fixing a bug, test
# Update: update a dependency, version
# Refactor: changes that do not change behavior
# Reformat: changes to formatting
# Document: changes to documentation
# Optimize: changes for performance

# body -----------------------------------------------------------------

# start with why
# use bullets
# e.g. - reformat JSON files with prettier

# footer ---------------------------------------------------------------

# closes #123, fixes #321, resolves org/repo#222

# be sure that each commit does one thing
# a pull request can have many single purpose commits
